      "updated": 1717420461375,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 118.27214032558751,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Phase One Tasks \n1. Create Company Channel\nOne For User and One For \nEmployee\n\n2.User visit company page \nit will join user company channel \n\n3.If Employee get login it will join\nemployee company channel\n\n4.On Employee join we update\nvalue to ets table of company\n\n5.Also broadcast changes to user\non company detail page\n\n6.We update company detail Page\n\n7.Update respected page on employee \nleave or client leave\n\n8.Create Call Follow initiate by client\nand webrtc call flow.\n\n9. Handle Drop call either from client or \nemployee\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Phase One Tasks \n1. Create Company Channel\nOne For User and One For \nEmployee\n\n2.User visit company page \nit will join user company channel \n\n3.If Employee get login it will join\nemployee company channel\n\n4.On Employee join we update\nvalue to ets table of company\n\n5.Also broadcast changes to user\non company detail page\n\n6.We update company detail Page\n\n7.Update respected page on employee \nleave or client leave\n\n8.Create Call Follow initiate by client\nand webrtc call flow.\n\n9. Handle Drop call either from client or \nemployee\n\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 4243
    },
