      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 118.27214032558751,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Phase 2 Tasks \n1. Handle Employee Reject Call\n\n2. Handle cases of page refresh either\nin call or initiate phase on both client\nand employee side\n\n3. Add Client Queue Functionality\n\n.....\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
