      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1717420461379,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Entities\n\n1. Company Server Basically Per Comapany Genserver start on app \nstart and more can be add dynamically under dynamic supervisor.\nOne Dynamic Superviosor which is under main Supervisor hold \nevery comapny genserver.For time this genserver hold company state\ne.g online_employees, client_queue, company_status, active_calls etc\n\n2. Then we have for channels\n    1. Client Channel(every client connect to this channel on login)\n    2. Employee Channel(every employee connect to it on login)\n    3. Client Company Channel(every client connect to it when visit company detail page)\n    4. Employee Company Channel(every employee connect to it on login)\n\n\n3. CompanyServerData module which contain all the business logic for manuplating\nthe company server state(should containt data struct but not implemented yet)\n\n\n\n\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Entities\n\n1. Company Server Basically Per Comapany Genserver start on app \nstart and more can be add dynamically under dynamic supervisor.\nOne Dynamic Superviosor which is under main Supervisor hold \nevery comapny genserver.For time this genserver hold company state\ne.g online_employees, client_queue, company_status, active_calls etc\n\n2. Then we have for channels\n    1. Client Channel(every client connect to this channel on login)\n    2. Employee Channel(every employee connect to it on login)\n    3. Client Company Channel(every client connect to it when visit company detail page)\n    4. Employee Company Channel(every employee connect to it on login)\n\n\n3. CompanyServerData module which contain all the business logic for manuplating\nthe company server state(should containt data struct but not implemented yet)\n\n\n\n\n",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 977
    },
