      "text": "Company server find employee active call if any .if call found broadcast to\nclient to also let him know about drop call br_en_call_drop and \nbroadcast updated state both employee and client company channels. \nif call not found then simply broadcast updated state to both employee \nand client. State update include online employee list, reevaluate company \nstatus, idle employee count, as well as active calls.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Company server find employee active call if any .if call found broadcast to\nclient to also let him know about drop call br_en_call_drop and \nbroadcast updated state both employee and client company channels. \nif call not found then simply broadcast updated state to both employee \nand client. State update include online employee list, reevaluate company \nstatus, idle employee count, as well as active calls.",
