      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Company Server call on_drop_call from comapny server data that clear \nactive call state mean remove entry. set employee status back to idle \nalso update idle_employee +1 and revaluate company status this \nprocess is same on drop call either by client or employee.Then \nCompany server boradcast message to clienht id if drop by employee and \nvice versa  br_en_call_drop",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Company Server call on_drop_call from comapny server data that clear \nactive call state mean remove entry. set employee status back to idle \nalso update idle_employee +1 and revaluate company status this \nprocess is same on drop call either by client or employee.Then \nCompany server boradcast message to clienht id if drop by employee and \nvice versa  br_en_call_drop",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
