      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Employee Channel send this message to Company Server than\nCompany Server Update State and then Company Server \nbroad cast this message with SDP and Employee Id to\nclient channel client channel utilize sdp and also join call\nchannel with the use of employee id. Now this call channel \nis main to hold call state if client or employee leave channel \ncall drop and also this channel hold the manipulation of state\nin ETS like on drop call explicitly or implicitly\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Employee Channel send this message to Company Server than\nCompany Server Update State and then Company Server \nbroad cast this message with SDP and Employee Id to\nclient channel client channel utilize sdp and also join call\nchannel with the use of employee id. Now this call channel \nis main to hold call state if client or employee leave channel \ncall drop and also this channel hold the manipulation of state\nin ETS like on drop call explicitly or implicitly\n",
